        },
        {
          "character": "张飞",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "原来如此。想俺二哥，既然败至麦城，为何不到上鄘，借兵相助？"
        },
        {
          "character": "廖化",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哎吓三千岁吓！二千岁也曾命廖化，去到上鄘，搬兵求救。怎奈刘封，坐观成\n败，不肯发兵，并将末将赶出帐外。"
        },
        {
          "character": "张飞",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "就是他！"
        },
        {
          "character": "廖化",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "正是。"
        },
        {
          "character": "张飞",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "小奴才吓！"
        },
        {
          "character": "张飞",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "听一言来怒气生，\n大骂刘封小畜牲！\n你竟胆敢不发兵。\n他是尔的什么人。\n我不杀你气怎平！"
        },
        {
          "character": "张飞",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "刘封这小奴才，如此丧心昧良，俺老张岂肯与你甘休。\n来，起兵前往！"
        },
        {
          "character": "俺二哥麦城被兵困、你手抚胸膛想一想、越思越想心头恨、廖化",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "且慢！"
        },
        {
          "character": "张飞",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "廖将军为何阻拦？"
        },
        {
          "character": "廖化",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "想那刘封，有我主赐他尚方斩杀宝剑，又有九头狮子鱼耳印。三千岁此番前去，\n只怕画虎不成，反类犬也。"
        },
        {
          "character": "张飞",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "将军但放宽心，俺老张自有道理。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（廖化暗下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "张飞",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "众将官，兵发上鄘武印山。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（四上手同允。〖泣颜回〗。众人同下。）"
        }
      ],
