    {
      "scene_index": 2,
      "label": "第二场",
      "characters_present": [
        "刘封",
        "四上手",
        "张飞",
        "旗牌"
      ],
      "lines": [
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（四龙套、四大铠、刘封同上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘封",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "营门战鼓响，军士赛虎狼。"
        },
        {
          "character": "旗牌",
          "line_type": "内白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "三千岁到！"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘封",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "有请。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（四龙套、四上手、旗牌引张飞同上。〖吹打〗。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘封",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "参见三叔父。"
        },
        {
          "character": "张飞",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "罢了。一旁坐下。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘封",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "三叔父多日不见，身体可好？"
        },
        {
          "character": "张飞",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "为叔的倒好，你可好？"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘封",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "侄儿尚好。但不知叔父，打从何处而来？"
        },
        {
          "character": "张飞",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "咱老子打从成都而来。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘封",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "既从成都而来，我父王身体可好？"
        },
        {
          "character": "张飞",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你父甚是安泰。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘封",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我那二叔父，现在荆州不知身体安泰否？"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（张飞做沉吟。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "张飞",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "这个奴才，他倒同我装起傻来了。\n刘封，你还不知么？"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘封",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "小侄不知吓。"
        },
        {
          "character": "张飞",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你二叔父，兵败麦城，已在玉泉山前，归天去了！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（刘封做惊骇。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘封",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "吓！我二叔父，怎么归天了？"
        },
        {
          "character": "张飞",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "只因孙权，遣诸葛瑾前来提亲，你二叔父不允，将他赶出了营外。不想他在孙\n权面前，搬动是非，联合曹操，故而全军覆没。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘封",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "既然如此，待侄儿发兵，前去与我二叔父报仇。"
        },
        {
          "character": "张飞",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "且慢！"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘封",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "三叔父为何阻拦？"
        },
        {
          "character": "张飞",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我且问你，你这上鄘城，有多少人马？"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘封",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "现有十万雄兵。"
        },
        {
          "character": "张飞",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "既有十万雄兵，却也不少。今日为叔的，要帮助与你。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘封",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "三叔帮助，必定成功。"
        },
        {
          "character": "张飞",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "但是一件。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘封",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哪一件？"
        },
        {
          "character": "张飞",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "必须将尚方斩杀宝剑、九头狮子鱼耳印，交付俺老张，方可前去。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘封",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "倘若杀退孙、曹两路兵将，三叔还要交付侄儿才好。"
        },
        {
          "character": "张飞",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "那是自然。看印拜过！\n（刘封抱剑举印。〖牌子〗。张飞拜，刘封拔剑欲杀张飞，退。张飞起，接印、剑，刘封拜，张飞欲杀刘封，\n退。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘封",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "印、剑也交付三叔，望三叔传令起兵。"
        },
        {
          "character": "张飞",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "慢来，慢来。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘封",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "却是为何？"
        },
        {
          "character": "张飞",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "为叔的还有一言，要同我儿言讲。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘封",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "叔父有何金言，当面请讲。"
        },
        {
          "character": "张飞",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "咱老张打从成都而来，见你父年迈，只恐不久人世。倘若晏驾，这汉室江山，\n不知何人承袭？"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘封",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "倘若我父王晏驾，这江山定是阿斗的了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "张飞",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "不能，不能！"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘封",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "为何不能？"
        },
        {
          "character": "张飞",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "想那阿斗，年轻幼小，怎能坐得江山？他是不能得够。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘封",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "阿斗年幼，不能执掌江山，只怕就要让与关兴坐了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "张飞",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "关兴正在服孝之中，不能登基继位。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘封",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "关兴不能，还有三叔父的儿子张苞，也坐得。"
        },
        {
          "character": "张飞",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "俺乃异姓之人，也不能坐。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘封",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "如此说来，这江山竟无人可坐了。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（张飞哭。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "张飞",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "只怕这江山，就、就是我儿你的了！"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘封",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "小侄若坐，只恐满朝文武不服。"
        },
        {
          "character": "张飞",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "说什么满朝文武不服。你今既有十万雄兵，待老夫帮助与你，倘有不服者，即\n按军法从事。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘封",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "倘能叔父替侄儿保驾，侄儿登了大宝，定封叔父为一字并肩王之位。"
        },
        {
          "character": "张飞",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "好！好！好！据俺老张看来，事不宜迟，倒不如点动人马，先到成都，将你父\n王刺死，我儿就可身登大宝，你看如何？"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘封",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "此事可以做得么？"
        },
        {
          "character": "张飞",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "做得的。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘封",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "如此就起兵前往。"
        },
        {
          "character": "张飞",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "且慢。为叔的有一计在此。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘封",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "有何妙计？"
        },
        {
          "character": "张飞",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "为叔的有一铜鼓，将你装在鼓内，就说是外国进来之宝，你父那时定要观看，\n待为叔在一旁，一鞭将鼓打开，你就势一刀，可就将你父刺死了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘封",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "此计甚好！"
        },
        {
          "character": "张飞",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "众将官，起兵蝎子山。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（众人同允。〖水龙吟〗。众人同走圆场。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "张飞",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "来，将铜鼓抬上来。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（四上手抬鼓同上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "张飞",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我儿藏在鼓内。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（刘封脱衣去盔，四上手推刘封入鼓内。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "张飞",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "众将官！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（众人同允。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "张飞",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "将鼓与我掷于山下！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（四上手同抛鼓。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "四上手",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "刘封尸骨碎如齑粉！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（张飞三笑。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "张飞",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "刘封已死，方解俺老张心头之恨！\n众将官，去往成都，待俺报与大哥知道便了。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（〖牌子〗，〖尾声〗。众人同下。）"
        }
      ],
      "interactions": [
